2.10	Betrayal_of_the_Left	Betrayal of the Left	Betrayal of the Left (full title: Betrayal of the Left: an Examination &amp; Refutation of Communist Policy from October 1939 to January 1941: with Suggestions for an Alternative and an Epilogue on Political Morality) was a book of essays published in 3 March 1941 by the Left Book Club, edited and largely written by Victor Gollancz.	
